test block with placeholder [[{ _ -> do; };]] 0 warnings 0 errors
test block with multiple placeholders [[{ _, _ -> do; };]] 0 warnings 0 errors
test block with some placeholders [[{ a, _ -> do; };]] 0 warnings 0 errors
